om/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Shadow-Of-The-Colossus-soundtrack.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Shadow-Of-The-Colossus-soundtrack-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Shadow-Of-The-Colossus-soundtrack-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Shadow-Of-The-Colossus-soundtrack-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Shadow-Of-The-Colossus-soundtrack-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Shadow-Of-The-Colossus-soundtrack-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> A scattering of video game soundtracks have been added to <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a> by <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony">Sony</a> , including <em>Gravity Rush, <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/shadow-of-the-colossus">Shadow Of The Colossus</a> , Soul Sacrifice</em> and more.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-bryan-intihar-marvels-spider-man-2-3516664">How Bryan Intihar made a video game masterpiece in &#39;Marvel&#39;s Spider-Man 2&#39;</a></strong></li></ul><p> The <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/1RjRHE0popjV7rhcHdp376/discography/album" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SIE Sound Team account on Spotify</a> is the one-stop shop for the soundtracks to a selection of the most acclaimed games on PlayStation, such as <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/astro-bot-rescue-mission">Astro Bot Rescue Mission</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bloodborne">Bloodborne</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/demons-souls">Demon&#39;s Souls</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-last-guardian">The Last Guardian</a></em> and more.</p><p> With this recently released lot, fans will be able to listen to the soundtracks to <em>Echochrome, Fantavision, Freedom Wars, Gravity Rush, Patchwork Heroes, PoPoLoCrois, popolocrois: a new departure, PoPoRoGue, Shadow Of The Colossus, Soul Sacrifice, What Did I Do To Deserve This, My Lord!? 1 &amp; 2, White Knight Chronicles, White Knight Chronicles 2</em> and <em>Wild Arms</em> ( <a href="https://twitter.com/AniPlaylist/status/1715763817798410475?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">as pointed out by X user AniPlaylist</a> ). </p><figure id="attachment_3519733" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3519733" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3519733" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3519733" class="wp-caption-text"> A PlayStation 2 Credit: Nikita Kostrykin via Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> At the time of writing, these have not appeared on any other streaming services like <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/apple-music">Apple Music</a> , so it might be a matter of time before the aforementioned soundtracks become available elsewhere.</p><p> For fans of <em>Shadow Of The Colossus</em> , it is a boon that <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ShadowoftheColossus/comments/17e2qet/the_shadow_of_the_colossus_soundtrack_is_now_on/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">they no longer have to rely on YouTube</a> to listen to the soundtrack, which is one of the highlights of the reflective experience of playing the game.</p><p> In Jack Richardson&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/shadow-of-the-colossus-true-masterstroke-is-alienation-not-immersion-3067962">exploration of Team Ico&#39;s original action adventure</a> for <em>NME</em> &#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/remastered">Remastered column</a> , he argued that the emptiness and minimalism of the game&#39;s direction is specifically haunting in a way that is unique to the medium.</p><p> “Games have two stories: the one that takes place in the game and the story of us playing it. There&#39;s certainly an artistry behind combining these two as closely as possible, but it&#39;s not a necessary goal,” he said. </p><figure id="attachment_3519736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3519736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3519736" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-added-to-sony-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3519736" class="wp-caption-text"> A PlayStation 2 controller Credit: Curtis Berry via Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> “When we play <em>Colossus</em> , we&#39;re constantly challenged to interpret what&#39;s going on as we do it. We&#39;re pushed away even as we&#39;re drawn in. Wander doesn&#39;t need to gain new abilities, because the one growing isn&#39;t him but us.”</p><p> In other gaming news, veteran game designer Raph Koster claimed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/developers-hate-ai-but-its-a-necessary-evil-says-veteran-designer-3518742">the majority of developers don&#39;t like using artificial intelligence in game development</a> , but the process is too expensive without it.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/shadow-of-the-colossus-soundtrack-comes-to-spotify-after-17-years-3519679">&#39;Shadow Of The Colossus&#39; soundtrack comes to Spotify after 17 years</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
